data.description: HOLIDAY PRICE IS 999,999 FOR DECEMBER ONLY!  Want privacy? We have it! Priced $400,000 under recent appraisal - INSTANT EQUITY!  51.6 acres of mature trees, creek w/waterfall, gazebo by creek, greenbelt for taxes, trails for riding ATV's, tons of wildlife for hunting! Not alot of mowing around the home!  Awesome open living area w/FP ! Kitchen & dining are open to living area.  Beautiful cabinets! Large master suite tucked in back corner of home! Luxurious walk in shower w/double controls! 2 other bedrooms & bath on main level! Upstairs has huge bonus room, bath & another room could be office or 4th bedroom. 2 walk in attic spaces (1 could be finished) Screened porch & large deck! Great picnic area! ! Interior just painted so move in ready!  Perfect for livestock, vineyard or several acres of crops! 24x48 Pole Barn! Comcast internet! Don't miss this!!
